Do I have that much free time?

115
00:11:47,581 --> 00:11:51,417
Should I just put aside my schedule for today and hang out with them?

116
00:11:52,432 --> 00:11:56,184
I'll see them if that is alright. Is it?

117
00:11:57,077 --> 00:11:58,841
No.

118
00:12:06,956 --> 00:12:09,846
Sheesh! What kind of lawn is this?
 (T/N: Jan Di's name means "lawn", so it's a play on words)

119
00:12:10,582 --> 00:12:12,938
Nothing's going right.

120
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,991
