121
00:12:25,373 --> 00:12:28,090
Yes? It's me.

122
00:13:25,708 --> 00:13:27,970
What kind of mayor wants to meet at a place like this?

123
00:13:27,970 --> 00:13:30,580
Did he used to be an athlete?

124
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:32,480
I'm sorry.

125
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:35,320
It's not something you should have to apologize for.

126
00:13:39,443 --> 00:13:42,617
Hey yo! Have you been well?

127
00:13:42,617 --> 00:13:44,480
Long time no see.

128
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:49,840
You guys came?

129
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:53,009
If we want to meet Shinhwa Group's heir, the busiest man in the world,

130
00:13:53,009 --> 00:13:55,260
we have to come to you, otherwise we'd never be able to see you.

131
00:13:58,070 --> 00:14:00,000
It's nice to see you.

132
00:14:01,210 --> 00:14:02,900
Really?

133
00:14:03,988 --> 00:14:06,690
Because it doesn't seem like you're all that glad.

134
00:14:09,377 --> 00:14:12,914
What's wrong? We haven't seen each other in so long.

135
00:14:12,914 --> 00:14:15,704
Geum Jan Di came with us too.

136
00:14:15,704 --> 00:14:16,930
Actually, that's not quite right.

137
00:14:16,930 --> 00:14:19,520
She came before us, to see you.

138
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:21,760
You haven't seen her, have you?

139
00:14:21,769 --> 00:14:24,030
