148
00:15:03,710 --> 00:15:05,190
What do you mean?

149
00:15:05,820 --> 00:15:08,960
You guys meet and break up with girls too.

150
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:10,110
So, what's wrong with me doing the same thing?

151
00:15:10,110 --> 00:15:13,422
Am I not allowed to do so too?
Even if I meet and break up twenty times, I don't do it the way you did!

152
00:15:13,422 --> 00:15:15,943
- Yi Jung, calm down!
- Let go!

153
00:15:15,943 --> 00:15:19,492
You! What did you say when we tried to stop you in the past?

154
00:15:19,492 --> 00:15:22,130
You said a real man is someone that's responsible from the beginning to the end.

155
00:15:22,130 --> 00:15:24,510
