156
00:15:25,543 --> 00:15:30,130
By chance, did you guys think that she and I would be together forever?

157
00:15:30,130 --> 00:15:32,180
That jerk.

158
00:15:32,810 --> 00:15:36,531
Whose fault is it that Geum Jan Di can't swim anymore?!

159
00:15:40,228 --> 00:15:42,290
- Stand up!
- Yi Jung, calm down.

160
00:15:42,290 --> 00:15:46,250
Does it look like I can calm down? Do you hear what this jerk is saying?

161
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:48,570
You!

162
00:15:48,570 --> 00:15:50,910
Did you start that relationship thinking something like this wouldn't happen?

163
00:15:50,910 --> 00:15:56,768
I warned you not to be so rash, you cowardly bastard!

164
00:15:57,977 --> 00:16:00,070
What's with you guys?

165
00:16:00,070 --> 00:16:04,530
- Did you guys quit being my friends so you could become a group of Jan Di's protectors?
- Goo Joon Pyo.

166
00:16:04,530 --> 00:16:07,386
If you came here as my friends, then play and go.

167
00:16:07,386 --> 00:16:12,729
But if you came to just to talk about Geum Jan Di, then leave immediately.

168
00:16:16,520 --> 00:16:18,780
How is it that you've changed so much?

169
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,500
- 700,000.
- What?

170
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:28,990
In Shinhwa Corporation,

171
00:16:30,010 --> 00:16:33,540
those families I have to take responsibility for,

172
00:16:34,326 --> 00:16:36,877
are about 700,000.

173
00:16:39,377 --> 00:16:42,210
Try having 700,000 families' lives resting on your shoulders.

174
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:45,280
And see if you don't change.

175
00:17:13,810 --> 00:17:17,670
An invaluable challenge. An unimaginable reality.

176
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:22,840
Asia's Venice. Shinhwa stands for the legend.

177
00:17:22,840 --> 00:17:23,980
[Shinhwa]

178
00:17:43,170 --> 00:17:45,150
Is Joon Pyo alright?

179
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:52,003
What's wrong? Did something happen?

180
00:17:52,003 --> 00:17:57,393
It's okay. Except for the fact that he's become strange.

181
00:17:57,393 --> 00:17:58,830
Hey!

182
00:17:58,830 --> 00:18:01,646
Geum Jan Di has to know too.

183
00:18:01,646 --> 00:18:06,430
As you know, a lot of things have happened.

184
00:18:06,430 --> 00:18:09,070
Stress is no joke too.

185
00:18:10,477 --> 00:18:14,729
He says he won't see me?

186
00:18:14,729 --> 00:18:17,210
You, how did you?

187
00:18:17,210 --> 00:18:19,120
You knew about it?

188
00:18:26,459 --> 00:18:29,270
You don't have to worry too much.

189
00:18:30,260 --> 00:18:35,580
No matter what it is, I came to hear it from Goo Joon Pyo himself.

190
00:18:36,180 --> 00:18:38,730
I have to face it.

191
00:18:38,730 --> 00:18:41,340
You really are Geum Jan Di!

192
00:18:42,230 --> 00:18:45,460
Wow, the night air is so nice.

193
00:18:47,380 --> 00:18:49,316
- Do you remember?
- What?

194
00:18:49,316 --> 00:18:51,650
What we used to do here when we were younger?

195
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:02,660
Here.

196
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:07,020
Rock, paper, scissors!

197
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:11,215
- Rock, paper, scissors!
- Nice!

198
00:19:12,077 --> 00:19:16,410
Ji Hoo, you go that way. Jan Di you go that way, and I'll go this way!

199
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:27,811
Ten...Nine...Eight...

200
00:19:27,811 --> 00:19:33,180
Seven. Six. Five.

201
00:19:33,180 --> 00:19:38,510
Four. Three. Two.

202
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:40,230
ONE!

203
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:44,960
I'm coming to find you guys!

204
00:20:55,745 --> 00:20:58,270
Awaiting you in Venice,

205
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:01,420
The city of Lovers.

206
00:22:31,610 --> 00:22:33,640
As a friend, I have a favor to ask.

207
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:34,980
Say it.

208
00:22:34,980 --> 00:22:36,510
Just meet with her once.

209
00:22:36,510 --> 00:22:37,950
Why should I do that?

210
00:22:37,950 --> 00:22:40,020
I told you, it's a favor for a friend.

211
00:22:40,020 --> 00:22:43,010
And if I ask why you're asking that?

212
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:49,979
Because right now, that's all I can do.

213
00:22:51,550 --> 00:22:53,238
I'm going.

214
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:13,400
♫ Although I ask it to stop, to stop wherever it is ♫

215
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:17,930
♫ My heart keeps going to you ♫

216
00:23:17,930 --> 00:23:22,310
♫ You don't even listen, or give in ♫

217
00:23:22,310 --> 00:23:26,720
♫ Why is my love like this? ♫

218
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:31,330
♫ Counting each memory one by one ♫

219
00:23:31,330 --> 00:23:35,770
♫ My heart can't rest for even a moment ♫

220
00:23:35,770 --> 00:23:40,320
♫ It will only become a burden that's too much to handle ♫

221
00:23:40,320 --> 00:23:44,670
♫ Why can't I just throw it away? ♫

222
00:23:44,670 --> 00:23:49,220
♫ Something must have happened to my heart ♫

223
00:23:49,220 --> 00:23:53,730
♫ I must have become a fool blinded by love ♫

224
00:23:53,730 --> 00:23:58,240
♫ Just one place, everyday one place ♫

225
00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:03,340
