234
00:25:51,860 --> 00:25:53,200
Sunbae?

235
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,950
Sorry for waking you up.

236
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:57,310
What's wrong?

237
00:25:57,310 --> 00:25:58,820
