240
00:26:13,141 --> 00:26:15,000
We're here.

241
00:26:15,750 --> 00:26:17,190
What?

242
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:19,840
From here, you have to go by yourself.

243
00:26:21,010 --> 00:26:24,210
It should be there on that bridge.

244
00:26:24,210 --> 00:26:27,990
