248
00:27:42,280 --> 00:27:45,921
I was worried after hearing the news about your father.

249
00:27:45,921 --> 00:27:47,750
Thanks.

250
00:27:48,610 --> 00:27:50,310
So...

251
00:27:51,520 --> 00:27:54,170
You came all this way for that?

252
00:27:55,450 --> 00:27:58,226
I guess you're getting along well now.

253
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,783
What?

254
00:28:01,783 --> 00:28:04,860
As you can see, I'm doing great.

255
00:28:04,860 --> 00:28:07,530
And as you know, I'm very busy.

256
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:11,730
